title: Dog Vs Cat:Â Cute 'Ninja' Kitten Shows Doberman Who's Boss

json.text: A curious kitten launches a surprise attack on a bemused dog in an adorable bid for attention.
Two-month old kitten Sophie was found abandoned in a gas station restroom in British Columbia, Canada,
and adopted by kind-hearted Jessica Manning.
But after meeting Jessica's three-year-old doberman, Bishop, the new arrival attempted to set a few ground rules.
During the comical encounter, Bishop patiently endures Sophie's probing paws,
and Jessica hopes the pair will soon become firm friends after this memorable introduction.
